node.text:
[#TheHedgehogAtHome] Discovered another value-for-money Bento Set, this time from @PeachGardenSG. Each lunch box came with 2 desserts and a drink, all for S$9.90 nett!
.
The beef slices were surprisingly succulent and well-marinated. Even the mango sago had some fresh diced mangoes, pomelo and sago. And our desserts and drinks were double-secured to prevent spillage. 💯 effort.👍 Swipe ⬅️ for more pics (we ordered 5 sets).
.
PS: Pls let me know below if you have such similar good deals to recommend me! 😂
.
.
.
.
.
.

@tuoi18 Thank you Tuoi. Yes, very worth it! 😃
A box lunch that looks really delicious! Especially white fish is good👌🐠🍱😋💕
@lovehasnotimelimitnboundaries Yes, definitely! You can give them a try too! 😃
@makanwarrior Haha yes! I couldn't finish my food and kept the 2 desserts for tea break and supper. 😆
@michelevenlee Indeed Michele, you'll definitely like it! 👍
@jesqleeyogawithlove IKR... You cna also give itna try, Jesq! 👍
